381
00:22:37,450 --> 00:22:38,542
Appelle-le.

382
00:22:39,419 --> 00:22:40,647
Merci, Ari.

383
00:22:41,654 --> 00:22:45,420
Trois auditions.
Pas besoin de faire le serveur.

384
00:22:49,128 --> 00:22:51,119
<i> Gary Busey .</i>

385
00:22:51,865 --> 00:22:54,333
Comment ça va ? Content de te voir, Ari.

386
00:22:54,834 --> 00:22:56,392
